Content: I am a casual average player!NLI have started a clan called WiB (Written in Blood)NLNLWe are an extremely new clan NLNLHere are our rules:NL- Any platformNL- Must be active on Discord and FortniteNL- Must change name to WiB or WiB_ at the start of your Fortnite nameNL - Ages 10-21NL- NAE serversNL- Tryout by build battling WiB WeaklyRich NLNLWe take anyone in the fortnite server but must tryout to be in the clan OFFICIALLY.
